h-century military history of the United States]]\n[[Category:20th-century aircraft shootdown incidents]]\n[[Category:Operations involving American special forces|Mogadishu]]\n[[Category:Pakistan military presence in other countries]]\n[[Category:Pakistan\u2013Somalia relations]]\n[[Category:20th century in Mogadishu]]\n[[Category:October 1993 events in Africa]]\n[[Category:Somali Civil War]]\n[[Category:Aviation accidents and incidents in Somalia]]\n", "name_user": "108.39.77.46", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(HHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHH)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Battle_of_Mogadishu_(1993)"}
