governed segments =\n}}  \n'''Changanassery State assembly constituency''' ({{lang-ml|\u0d1a\u0d19\u0d4d\u0d19\u0d28\u0d3e\u0d36\u0d4d\u0d36\u0d47\u0d30\u0d3f \u0d28\u0d3f\u0d2f\u0d2e\u0d38\u0d2d\u0d3e \u0d28\u0d3f\u0d2f\u0d4b\u0d1c\u0d15 \u0d2e\u0d23\u0d4d\u0d21\u0d32\u0d02}}) is one of the 140 [[Kerala Legislative Assembly|state legislative assembly]] constituencies at the state [[Kerala]] in southern [[India]]. It is also one of the 7 [[Kerala Legislative Assembly|state legislative assembly]] constituencies included in the [[Mavelikara (Lok Sabha constituency)|Mavelikara Lok Sabha constituency]].<ref>{{cite web\n | url = https://kottayam.nic.in/constituencies\n | website = kottayam.nic.in\n | title = State Assembly Constituencies in Kottayam district\n |accessdate  =16 March 2020\n}}</ref>\n\n== Members of Legislative Assembly ==\nThe following list contains all members of [[Kerala Legislative Assembly]] who have represented the constituency:\n\n'''Key'''\n\n{{Party index link|Kerala Congress (Mani)}}   \n{| class=\"sortable\" width=\"50%\" cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"1\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border: 2px #000000 solid; font-size: x-big;\"\n! style=\"background-color:#666666; color:white\" |Election\n! style=\"background-color:#666666; color:white\" |Niyama\nSabha\n! style=\"background-color:#666666; color:white\" |Member\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#666666; color:white\" |Party\n! style=\"background-color:#666666; color:white\" |Tenure\n|-\n|[[2011 Kerala Legislative Assembly election|2011]]\n|13th\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[C. F. Thomas]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Kerala Congress (M)|KC(M)]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: {{Kerala Congress (Mani)/meta/color}}\" |\n|2011 \u2013 2016\n|-\n|[[2016 Kerala Legislative Assembly election|2016]]\n|14th\n|Incumbent\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[Changanassery]]\n* [[Kottayam district]]\n* [[List of constituencies of the Kerala Legislative Assembly]]\n* [[2016 Kerala Legislative Assem